name: Gary V. FINCK v. AETNA CASUALTY & SURETY CO.
name_abbreviation: Finck v. Aetna Casualty & Surety Co.

parties: Gary V. FINCK v. AETNA CASUALTY & SURETY CO.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiff’s motion to default as prayed is denied. The defendant’s motion to extend the time for filing its brief is granted and said brief shall be filed on or before December 5, 1979.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Hanson, Curran & Parks, David P. Whitman, Providence, for plaintiff.
Roberts, Carroll, Feldstein & Tucker, David W. Carroll, Providence, for defendant.
